Properties.Tag: Select [MON_K_UL_PARENT].[CUL] As [Распорядитель пользователя], Max([MON_K_UL_PARENT].[NUL]) As [Наименование распорядителя], [MON_K_UL].[CUL] As [Организация], Max([MON_K_UL].[NUL]) As [Наименование организации], [MON_K_ROLE_PARENT].[CROLE] As [Роль распорядителя пользовател], Max([MON_K_ROLE_PARENT].[NROLE]) As [Наименование типа распорядит], [MON_K_ROLE].[CROLE] As [Роль организации], Max([MON_K_ROLE].[NROLE]) As [Наименование роли организации] From (((([MON_K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) Inner Join [MON_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([MON_K_UL_K_UL].[MON_K_ULID]=[MON_K_UL].[MON_K_ULID])) Inner Join [MON_K_ROLE] With (NoLock) On ([MON_K_UL_K_UL].[MON_K_ROLEID]=[MON_K_ROLE].[MON_K_ROLEID])) Inner Join [MON_K_UL] As [MON_K_UL_PARENT] With (NoLock) On ([MON_K_UL_K_UL].[MON_K_ULID_PARENT]=[MON_K_UL_PARENT].[MON_K_ULID])) Inner Join [MON_K_ROLE] As [MON_K_ROLE_PARENT] With (NoLock) On ([MON_K_UL_K_UL].[MON_K_ROLEID_PARENT]=[MON_K_ROLE_PARENT].[MON_K_ROLEID])) Where |0 Group by [MON_K_UL_PARENT].[CUL], [MON_K_UL].[CUL], [MON_K_ROLE_PARENT].[CROLE], [MON_K_ROLE].[CROLE] Order by |1
